      • get

        public <T> OrchestrateRequest<KvList<T>> get(@NonNull
                                             java.lang.Class<T> clazz)
        Fetch a paginated, lexicographically ordered list of items contained in a collection.

        Usage:

         
 KvList<String> objects =
         client.listCollection("someCollection")
               .limit(10)
               .get(String.class)
               .get();
        Type Parameters:
        T - The type to deserialize the result of the request to.
        Parameters:
        clazz - Type information for marshalling objects at runtime.
        Returns:
        The prepared get request.
